---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'

const title = 'Privacy Policy — ReplyPals'
const description = 'How ReplyPals collects, uses, and protects your data.'
const canonicalUrl = 'https://replypals.in/privacy'
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}>
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-4 px-4 py-12 text-slate-700">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-600">Last updated: April 5, 2026</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      We collect your email address when you create an account, usage counts to enforce plan limits, and an anonymous
      identifier for users who try the product before signing up. Payment and billing information is processed by our
      payment provider (Stripe) and is not stored on our servers in full.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">How we store data</h2>
    <p>
      Data is stored in Supabase (PostgreSQL) with encryption in transit (TLS) and at rest where supported by the
      infrastructure provider. Access is restricted to operational needs.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">What we do not store</h2>
    <p>
      The full content of your rewrites is not logged permanently for product improvement. We may retain minimal metadata
      (for example counts, timestamps, and error codes) to operate quotas and diagnose issues.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Deleting your account</h2>
    <p>
      You can request deletion of your account and associated profile data by contacting us at the email below. We will
      confirm identity and complete deletion within a reasonable period, subject to legal retention requirements.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions: <a href="mailto:privacy@replypals.in" class="text-indigo-700 hover:underline">privacy@replypals.in</a>
    </p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
